{
  "stem": "27509.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And all the-- the knitting was done on a fully fashioned basis because nobody ever dreamt of needing a square piece of cloth, and then cut away because the yarn was too valuable to be contemplated to be cut away and thrown away.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But once the overlocker came about, which had sewing and cutting as one activity, because that was the nature of the overlocker, then the entire thing changed in terms of production.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And all the changed in terms of the number of people involved and employed, because one overlocker did the work of many other workers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But-- so it had the pride of place in that little corner behind one of the-- of the beds in that little nook sat a woman overlocker.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that was a place revered and-- and respected, because nobody-- the children didn't dare come too close and interfere with such a valuable piece of-- of the-- the latest equipment.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the-- the domestic lived, of course-- slept in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was a sort of a wooden bank sort of thing which turned into a sleeping bed for night time, and then the daytime it used to have a cover on top.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that was working space for-- for the women to do their kitchen activities on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I would think that in the-- in the work-- in the-- in the knitting room, there must have been six, seven, eight people there permanently.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mind you, also night shift.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We have been-- the-- the of machines was limited.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The investment in knit was a major burden.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The-- and because most of it was hand driven, the-- these flat knitting machines were driven by hand in the early days.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the production was very slow.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
